paragraphs.title: 大盘指数获取和转换
paragraphs.text:
import tushare as ts
import pandas as pd

import datetime
import matplotlib as mpl
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

from matplotlib.dates import DateFormatter, WeekdayLocator, DayLocator, MONDAY,YEARLY,date2num
from matplotlib.finance import quotes_historical_yahoo_ohlc, candlestick_ohlc

def df2tab(pdf_index):
    a ="""%table\r index\t code\t name\t change\t open\t preclose\t close\t high\r """
    for idx in pdf_index.index:
        a = a + str(idx) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['code']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['name']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['change']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['open']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['preclose']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['close']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['high']) + "\r"
    return a

def getIndex_All():
    df = ts.get_index()
    return df2tab(df)

paragraphs.title: 专项指数获取和转换
paragraphs.text:
# 转换指数，从pandas到%table    
def ind2tab(pdf_index):
    a ="""%table\r index\t date\t open\t close\t high\t low\t volume\r """
    for idx in pdf_index.index:
        a = a + str(idx) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['date']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['open']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['close']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['high']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['low']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['volume']) + "\r"
    return a

# 获得指数，返回（pandas.DataFrame,str-%tab）的二元组。
def getind(indcode):
    df_index = ts.get_k_data(indcode, index=True)
    df_index.index = df_index['date']
    indata = ind2tab(df_index)
    return (df_index,indata)

# 创建综合指数的时间序列表。
zhshu=pd.DataFrame(index=shzz_index.index)
zhshu.index=shzz_index.date

# 将各个指数表的high列加入综合指数表。
zhshu['SHZZ']=shzz_index['high']
zhshu['CYBZ']=cybz_index['high']

# 综合指数表转为Tab格式
def all_ind2tab(pdf_index):
    a ="""%table\r index\t SHZZ\t CYBZ\r"""
    for idx in pdf_index.index:
        a = a + str(idx) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['SHZZ']) + "\t" \
            + str(pdf_index.ix[idx]['CYBZ']) + "\r" 
    return a

def getIndexTrend():
    return all_ind2tab(zhshu)
